title: Villmark(Dark Woods)[2003]DVDRIP[Nor]
description:
The crew of the TV show "Real TV" with controlling boss Gunnar on the front line will soon begin production of a reality show for which participants are selected to survive in the wilderness.
To test his new employees, Gunnar takes them to a remote log cabin. Soon the team experiences some escalating incidents which lead to paranoia, accusations and mistrust.
